I led with Electrode, who has one weakness, which is ground. 5/7 of the times I tested this my oppenent led with a ground type. I then switched to Alolan sandslash, a steel/ice type, which is 4x weak to fire and fighting types, but it is super effective against ground. 4/4 times my opponent led with a fire or fighting type. This system is horrendous. Do not play.
